<EnemyInfo>
  <Name>Snail</Name>
  <Description>
    A shelled crawler that moves along the wall following the room geometry. A lot of the crawling enemies share the same code. Unlike the other crawlers, the snail will fall and bounce around if shot. It will stop moving if samus and the snail are facing each other. While not moving, the snail because solid.

    When bouncing around, it uses the move speed set at $A3:D2BE. The value uses the same index add the Speed parameter.
  </Description>
